                  <div id="dnn_ctr13645_HtmlModule_lblContent">
                     <h2>Main attractions</h2>
                     <p>Tianjin is filled with a wide variety of attractions to explore, including:</p>
                     <ul>
                        <li>Ancient Cultural Street</li>
                        <li>Huangyaguan Great Wall</li>
                        <li>Water Park</li>
                        <li>Mt. Panshan Scenic Area</li>
                        <li>Haihe River</li>
                     </ul>
