                  <div id="dnn_ctr13643_HtmlModule_lblContent">
                     <h2>Working while studying</h2>
                     <p>While studying at Nankai University, you’ll most likely have the opportunity to get involved in an internship or a work placement. Tianjin is the perfect location for this, with 285 Fortune 500 companies in the city including Samsung, Toyota, Yamaha, Motorola and more. And just half an hour away from Beijing by bullet train, you’ll have many more employment options nearby too. </p>
                  </div>
